import { Route, Routes } from "react-router"
import { Login1 } from "../allComponent/Login1"
import { Login2 } from "../allComponent/Login2"



export const Routing = () => {

    return <>
        <Routes>
            <Route path="Home"></Route>
            <Route path='Login1' element={<Login1></Login1>}></Route>
            <Route path='' element={<Login1></Login1>}></Route>
            <Route path='Login2' element={<Login2></Login2>}></Route>
        </Routes>

    </>
}
